WEBVTT

00:02.000 --> 00:05.680
This programme contains some
violent scenes and strong language

00:05.680 --> 00:06.720
There's been another murder. I have
worries it's the same guy.

00:06.720 --> 00:09.560
I know where you live.
Like I've never heard that before.

00:13.120 --> 00:16.200
'You think her hair's been
clipped? Where?'

00:17.560 --> 00:18.680
There.

00:18.680 --> 00:22.560
'She has a high level of chorionic
gonadotropin in her blood.

00:22.560 --> 00:24.240
'I'm thinking she was pregnant.'

00:24.240 --> 00:25.840
Make me SIO.

00:25.840 --> 00:29.120
'This is the third
murder in three months, Jim.'

00:29.120 --> 00:32.320
Is this the body of your daughter
Sarah Kay?

00:32.320 --> 00:34.120
What are you doing?!

00:34.120 --> 00:36.960
'If we don't stop him he will
kill again.'

00:36.960 --> 00:39.240
Excuse me? Is this your purse?

00:40.480 --> 00:42.120
Oh, erm, thank you so much.

00:50.720 --> 00:51.880
DOOR OPENS

